DEVIATIONS
Changes made by Hanzo AI, Inc. relative to upstream Argo CD v3.4.5, per
Apache-2.0 Section 4(b):

- Repackaged from the Go module github.com/argoproj/argo-cd/v3 to
  github.com/hanzoai/deploy/v3. The /v3 major suffix is retained so release
  tags stay in correspondence with the upstream v3 lineage a release is cut
  from, which is what keeps upstream security advisories answerable against
  our builds. Behaviour is unchanged by the rename.

- Container images are built by Hanzo CI on Hanzo runners and published to
  ghcr.io/hanzoai/deploy, rather than quay.io/argoproj/argocd.

- Product name is Hanzo CD.
